Class JSONUtils.CommonDataJSONObject

Enclosing class:
JSONUtils
public static class JSONUtils.CommonDataJSONObject extends JSONObject implements AutoCloseable
Provides a wrapper around JSONObject that allows saving and restoring its values to/from the common data folder (saves/common). Use this to have global settings that persist between saves.
Since:
2.4
